---
// About section: asymmetric layout — Elyse "About" style
---
<section id="about" class="relative py-24 sm:py-32 overflow-hidden" style="background: var(--dark);">

  <div class="section-divider"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-10 lg:px-14">

    <!-- Label -->
    <div class="mb-12 sm:mb-16" data-reveal>
      <span class="section-label">(Sobre a Cyllor)</span>
    </div>

    <!-- Main grid: left text + center photo + right text -->
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1.1fr_1fr] gap-10 lg:gap-8 items-center mb-20 lg:mb-28">

      <!-- Left: large italic headline -->
      <div data-reveal="left" data-delay="100">
        <h2 class="font-display font-light leading-tight mb-6" style="font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 4.5rem); color: var(--cream);">
          <span class="italic" style="color: var(--gold);">Gestão eficiente</span><br/>
          sem complicações.
        </h2>
        <p class="font-mono text-[0.6rem] tracking-[0.22em] uppercase mb-4" style="color: var(--muted);">Tecnologia para síndicos</p>
        <div class="h-px w-16" style="background: rgba(201,169,110,0.4);"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Center: photo -->
      <div class="img-zoom rounded-sm overflow-hidden aspect-[3/4] lg:aspect-auto lg:h-[580px]" data-reveal="scale" data-delay="50">
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1545324418-cc1a3fa10c00?w=900&q=85&auto=format&fit=crop"
          alt="Área comum de condomínio moderno"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Right: description -->
      <div data-reveal="right" data-delay="150">
        <p class="font-body text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed mb-6" style="color: rgba(240,235,225,0.6); line-height: 1.8;">
          Cada detalhe da Cyllor reflete um compromisso com a excelência operacional. Da comunicação entre moradores ao controle de acesso, a plataforma une todos os módulos em um fluxo claro e previsível.
        </p>
        <p class="font-body text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: rgba(240,235,225,0.6); line-height: 1.8;">
          Seja um condomínio clube, residencial ou de médio porte, a Cyllor reduz retrabalho, conflitos e a dependência de grupos dispersos.
        </p>

        <!-- Gold line accent -->
        <div class="mt-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <div class="h-px flex-1" style="background: rgba(201,169,110,0.2);"></div>
          <span class="font-mono text-[0.55rem] tracking-widest uppercase" style="color: var(--gold);">Cyllor</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats row — Elyse numbers style -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-10 lg:gap-6 pt-12 border-t" style="border-color: rgba(201,169,110,0.12);">

      <div data-reveal data-delay="0">
        <p class="font-display font-light leading-none mb-3" style="font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 5.5rem); color: var(--cream);">
          2–4<span class="text-2xl" style="color: var(--gold);"> sem</span>
        </p>
        <p class="font-mono text-[0.58rem] tracking-[0.22em] uppercase leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted);">
          implantação assistida<br/>sem depender de improviso
        </p>
      </div>

      <div data-reveal data-delay="80">
        <p class="font-display font-light leading-none mb-3" style="font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 5.5rem); color: var(--cream);">
          1<span class="text-2xl" style="color: var(--gold);"> canal</span>
        </p>
        <p class="font-mono text-[0.58rem] tracking-[0.22em] uppercase leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted);">
          comunicação centralizada<br/>para gestão e moradores
        </p>
      </div>

      <div data-reveal data-delay="160">
        <p class="font-display font-light leading-none mb-3" style="font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 5.5rem); color: var(--cream);">
          60<span class="text-2xl" style="color: var(--gold);">%</span>
        </p>
        <p class="font-mono text-[0.58rem] tracking-[0.22em] uppercase leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted);">
          redução de conflitos<br/>em reservas e acesso
        </p>
      </div>

      <div data-reveal data-delay="240">
        <p class="font-display font-light leading-none mb-3" style="font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 5.5rem); color: var(--cream);">
          24<span class="text-2xl" style="color: var(--gold);">/7</span>
        </p>
        <p class="font-mono text-[0.58rem] tracking-[0.22em] uppercase leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted);">
          histórico e registros<br/>sempre disponíveis
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
